ADD . $GOPATH/src/github.com/Depado/smallblog

RUN dep ensure -vendor-only

ARG version

# Define timezone
ENV TZ=Europe/Paris

# Define the ENTRYPOINT
WORKDIR /home
ENTRYPOINT ./smallblog

# Document that the service listens on port 8080.
EXPOSE 8080
